WEBVTT

01:34.480 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:43.160
NANWU UNIVERSITY

02:02.840 --> 02:05.760
Yan. Tomorrow is the First Frost
with a big drop in temperature,

02:05.840 --> 02:07.400
so remember to wear more clothes.

02:08.720 --> 02:09.840
Shuangjiang (the First Frost)?

02:14.160 --> 02:16.240
Did anyone say happy birthday to her?

02:21.280 --> 02:23.920
Hello. The number
you have dialed does not exist.

02:24.000 --> 02:25.400
Please check and dial again.

02:32.120 --> 02:35.040
Hello. The number you have dialed
does not exist.

02:35.120 --> 02:36.400
Please check and dial again.

02:42.640 --> 02:45.320
Hello. The number
you have dialed does not exist.

02:45.400 --> 02:46.880
Please check and dial again.

03:16.160 --> 03:17.960
WEN SHUANGJIANG

03:20.680 --> 03:23.320
Hello. The number
you have dialed does not exist.

03:23.400 --> 03:25.000
Please check and dial again.

03:53.560 --> 03:55.240
What are you doing?
Why aren't you sleeping?

03:58.360 --> 03:59.200
Throwing away my cell phone.

04:01.160 --> 04:02.000
Why?

04:06.600 --> 04:07.960
It's broken.

04:17.920 --> 04:18.920
Happy birthday.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.320
3,325 DAYS

04:45.400 --> 04:47.000
DAY 263 OF LIVING TOGETHER

04:47.080 --> 04:49.480
Zhang Xin's ex-boyfriend proposed to her.

04:49.560 --> 04:51.760
- Yeah.
- This National Holiday wasn't wasted.

04:51.840 --> 04:53.600
Now tell me.

04:53.680 --> 04:55.840
Actually, my current boyfriend
has been trying

04:55.920 --> 04:57.920
to get back together with me.

04:58.000 --> 04:59.200
I tell you what.

04:59.280 --> 05:03.160
When it comes to men,
you can't be subservient to them.

05:03.240 --> 05:03.960
Right.

05:04.040 --> 05:06.640
- Men?
- What's wrong with men?

05:06.720 --> 05:09.480
- I don't approve of what you're saying.
- Why don't you approve?

05:09.560 --> 05:10.560
I just don't approve.

05:10.640 --> 05:14.480
You can't use
that kind of tantalization on us.

05:14.560 --> 05:17.160
People are different, aren't they?

05:17.240 --> 05:18.280
Wait a minute.

05:19.920 --> 05:20.880
Wait a minute.

05:21.840 --> 05:23.400
I think my water just broke.

05:23.920 --> 05:25.280
What about that?

05:26.000 --> 05:27.560
Now. Fang Li.

05:27.640 --> 05:30.560
Call an ambulance.

05:30.640 --> 05:32.600
We'll wait outside.

05:33.120 --> 05:34.160
- Hold on.
- Hold on.

05:37.960 --> 05:39.160
Who's the father?

05:40.200 --> 05:41.720
Not me. I'm sorry.

05:42.800 --> 05:44.880
- How could I be?
- Doctor.

05:44.960 --> 05:48.200
She's a single mom.
She and her ex-husband just got divorced.

05:48.760 --> 05:50.320
Is there anything bad?

05:51.240 --> 05:53.040
Actually, the mother had a high-leak

05:53.120 --> 05:54.960
and didn't notice that her water broke.

05:55.040 --> 05:57.000
The baby's heartbeat is not so good.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.960
Both the baby
and the mother are in danger.

05:59.040 --> 06:01.640
We were hoping that the father would come
and help us persuade the mother

06:01.720 --> 06:02.880
to opt for a C-section,

06:02.960 --> 06:05.360
but the mother has always wanted
a normal delivery.

06:05.440 --> 06:08.280
So, can you let us go in
and talk her through it?

06:08.360 --> 06:09.560
- Yes.
- At this stage,

06:09.640 --> 06:12.800
it's best for the mother and her husband
to discuss and decide together.

06:12.880 --> 06:16.080
So, keep trying to contact him.
Don't worry. We'll try.

06:16.160 --> 06:17.600
- I'll go in then.
- Thank you.

06:17.680 --> 06:19.320
Thank you. Please.

06:19.840 --> 06:21.160
What to do?

06:26.080 --> 06:27.520
Where's Su Tian?

06:27.600 --> 06:28.760
Guo from the financial group.

06:28.840 --> 06:30.840
- Why are you here?
- What are you doing here?

06:30.920 --> 06:33.360
I got her call and rushed over.
How's it going? Is she in labor?

06:34.080 --> 06:35.160
Why are you so anxious?

06:35.240 --> 06:36.920
She's my girlfriend,
so how could I not be anxious?

06:37.000 --> 06:40.160
- You're the father of the baby?
- I'm not.

06:41.240 --> 06:44.040
Sorry. I kind of am.

06:44.120 --> 06:45.400
- What do you mean?
- What's…

06:45.480 --> 06:48.480
What's going on here?
Tell me exactly what's going on.

06:49.840 --> 06:51.440
Your cervix is not
dilated enough right now.

06:51.520 --> 06:54.120
If the labor takes too long,
it's not good for you or the baby,

06:54.200 --> 06:56.680
and in the end, we'll probably
end up with a C-section.

06:57.720 --> 06:58.960
Then I'll try again.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.240
- Okay.
- Come on. Try together.

07:00.320 --> 07:01.320
Come on.

07:01.880 --> 07:03.680
I've had a crush on her for a long time.

07:04.200 --> 07:06.640
I didn't dare to court her
until she got divorced,

07:07.480 --> 07:09.920
but I didn't realize she was pregnant,

07:10.680 --> 07:12.360
and the guy was irresponsible,

07:13.280 --> 07:14.480
but it's okay.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.040
I'm willing to take care
of her and her baby.

07:30.240 --> 07:32.960
Come on. Congratulations.
It's a little girl.

07:33.640 --> 07:36.080
Take a look. Look at her. She's so cute.

07:36.600 --> 07:39.120
She looks just like you.
Just as cute as her mom.

07:50.040 --> 07:51.320
MATERNITY WARD

07:51.400 --> 07:52.600
- Here they come.
- Su Tian.

07:53.640 --> 07:54.840
- How are you doing?
- Did that hurt?

07:54.920 --> 07:57.360
- Are you okay? Is the baby all right?
- You know what?

07:57.440 --> 07:59.800
I came as soon as you got in,
but they wouldn't let me in.

07:59.880 --> 08:01.400
They said I wasn't the baby's father.

08:03.320 --> 08:04.880
I wanted to go in to be with you.

08:05.680 --> 08:06.960
Su Tian.

08:10.200 --> 08:11.640
I'll take care of this child.

08:13.280 --> 08:15.480
I'll love her as if she were my own,

08:16.360 --> 08:17.920
and even when she grows up,

08:18.000 --> 08:20.280
we'll tell her how much we love her.

08:23.280 --> 08:26.840
The baby isn't mine,
but it doesn't matter.

08:28.600 --> 08:30.400
I'll take care of you and the baby.

08:39.679 --> 08:41.799
OK. Let's get her to rest.

08:41.880 --> 08:42.720
We should then…

08:42.799 --> 08:44.039
- Right.
- Go to the ward now.

08:44.120 --> 08:45.040
Let's get her rested up.

08:45.120 --> 08:46.000
- OK.
- She's tired.

08:51.720 --> 08:53.200
- Now have a rest.
- Yes.

08:53.280 --> 08:54.600
As long as she's okay.

08:54.680 --> 08:56.600
Do you want a boy or a girl?

08:57.120 --> 08:58.040
Why do you ask all of a sudden?

08:58.120 --> 08:59.600
I'm just curious.

08:59.680 --> 09:00.960
I don't think it matters.

09:01.040 --> 09:03.320
By the way,
is Su Tian having a boy or a girl?

09:03.400 --> 09:06.000
- I forgot to ask. I'll ask.
- Yes, ask now.

09:06.520 --> 09:07.600
- She's having a baby.
- Hello.

09:07.680 --> 09:10.200
Is Su Tian having a boy or a girl?

09:10.280 --> 09:12.400
My coworker just had a baby.

09:12.480 --> 09:14.200
SANG YAN - WEN YIFAN

09:15.600 --> 09:16.480
A girl.

09:16.560 --> 09:17.760
- Really?
- Why are you so happy?

09:17.840 --> 09:19.280
You're as happy as if
you gave birth to the baby.

09:19.360 --> 09:20.240
Aren't you happy?

09:20.320 --> 09:21.440
- Aren't you happy?
- I am.

09:21.520 --> 09:22.560
Ms. Qian must be happy.

09:22.640 --> 09:24.360
If you or you two are not happy,
you know what?

09:24.440 --> 09:25.640
I'll tell Tian and ask her to beat you up.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.240
- Congratulations.
- It's almost time

09:27.320 --> 09:28.840
to go to work.

09:28.920 --> 09:30.360
SANG YAN

09:30.440 --> 09:35.640
Life is really amazing, isn't it?

09:35.720 --> 09:40.360
WEN YIFAN

09:51.240 --> 09:55.040
SHUANGJIANG

09:56.400 --> 09:57.440
Sir.

09:57.520 --> 10:00.000
Now you can think
about Woodie's favorite things

10:00.080 --> 10:01.840
and put them next to him.

10:01.920 --> 10:05.120
He'll know you love him and won't be sad.

10:08.600 --> 10:12.800
A CHANCE ENCOUNTER LASTS A LIFETIME

10:12.880 --> 10:13.920
Woodie.

10:14.880 --> 10:18.560
These are the things you like to eat.

10:20.040 --> 10:23.800
Don't eat too much,
or you will get bloated.

10:50.880 --> 10:53.600
Is there anything else
you'd like to say to Woodie?

10:56.160 --> 10:58.920
If not, I'll send him away.

11:15.280 --> 11:16.320
Woodie.

11:17.040 --> 11:18.280
Woodie, run.

11:19.320 --> 11:20.880
Woodie, run.

11:20.960 --> 11:23.280
Woodie, run. Woodie.

11:23.360 --> 11:25.360
Don't ever come back, Woodie.

11:37.920 --> 11:39.920
The day my parents
and my brother went to the funeral,

11:40.440 --> 11:41.760
Grandpa wouldn't let me go.

11:42.480 --> 11:44.800
I can't imagine how sad he was.

11:59.560 --> 12:06.200
YISHENG PET BURIAL

12:07.680 --> 12:09.240
Ma.

12:09.320 --> 12:11.440
Is that smoke Woodie?

12:13.200 --> 12:14.280
It's black.

12:15.480 --> 12:16.720
It could be.

12:34.760 --> 12:36.440
FATHER WEN LIANGZHE'S SPIRIT TABLET

12:39.840 --> 12:41.560
When my dad died,

12:42.760 --> 12:45.320
I used to wonder where he went,

12:52.360 --> 12:54.400
but when I looked
at the clouds in the sky,

12:56.080 --> 12:58.280
my dad's face would slowly come back.

13:01.080 --> 13:02.240
He was smiling.

13:02.760 --> 13:04.080
When I miss him,

13:04.840 --> 13:06.960
he's probably missing me, too.

13:07.480 --> 13:09.280
We're going to meet someday.

13:10.280 --> 13:12.280
They just get there before us

13:13.560 --> 13:17.200
and set up a warm home for us there.

13:32.680 --> 13:36.280
It's a blessing to be missed

13:37.240 --> 13:39.600
or remembered, isn't it?

13:44.040 --> 13:45.280
WILL YOU BE BACK LATE TODAY?

13:46.920 --> 13:50.760
I MIGHT

13:50.840 --> 13:51.680
JUST REST

14:03.400 --> 14:04.320
Grandpa.

14:06.480 --> 14:07.520
Keep this.

14:08.440 --> 14:10.320
You can think of him anytime.

14:34.920 --> 14:35.800
You're still awake.

14:42.960 --> 14:44.000
Wen Yifan.

14:45.200 --> 14:47.440
Give me the carton from the fridge.

15:44.520 --> 15:46.040
Then I'll go to bed now.

15:47.840 --> 15:49.040
Eat with me.

16:25.000 --> 16:27.200
Did you buy this just for me?

16:29.280 --> 16:30.160
Not for anyone.

16:37.480 --> 16:38.760
Thanks for that.

16:39.640 --> 16:40.560
So, you remember.

16:50.400 --> 16:51.280
Can I take a picture?

17:03.480 --> 17:06.480
Can I take a picture of you holding it?

17:09.119 --> 17:10.160
Holding it?

17:18.760 --> 17:19.920
With me?

17:39.120 --> 17:40.120
Make a wish.

18:03.760 --> 18:07.360
Happy birthday to you

18:08.280 --> 18:11.800
Happy birthday to you

18:12.320 --> 18:16.320
Happy birthday to you

18:16.920 --> 18:20.680
Happy birthday to you

18:21.480 --> 18:22.760
Make a wish.

18:47.400 --> 18:48.440
What did you wish for?

18:50.160 --> 18:51.800
If I say it, it won't come true.

18:55.560 --> 18:58.240
If you don't,
how can I make it come true for you?

19:05.680 --> 19:08.560
It's about work.

19:12.640 --> 19:13.480
Okay, fine.

19:13.560 --> 19:15.440
I thought you wanted me
to be your boyfriend.

19:44.720 --> 19:46.400
It's not good to eat
too many sweets at night.

20:09.280 --> 20:10.160
Nice.

20:32.840 --> 20:37.120
I'll put the rest in the fridge
and eat it tomorrow.

20:38.520 --> 20:39.360
Okay.

20:44.040 --> 20:45.160
Wen Yifan.

20:49.880 --> 20:52.600
The gift is on the shelf. Get it yourself.

21:35.000 --> 21:35.920
Happy birthday.

22:20.640 --> 22:21.720
Hello?

22:21.800 --> 22:24.800
Bro. My Woodie died.

22:30.480 --> 22:33.920
Are you okay?

22:35.600 --> 22:36.480
Yes.

22:38.880 --> 22:41.760
It's old, so we're prepared for it.

22:42.760 --> 22:44.400
Is there something else going on with you?

22:49.720 --> 22:50.840
I'm in love with someone.

22:53.040 --> 22:55.040
Seems nothing is going on.

22:55.560 --> 22:58.480
Do you still have time
to talk to me about your trifles?

22:58.560 --> 22:59.840
It's different this time.

23:01.480 --> 23:02.400
Sang Yan.

23:02.480 --> 23:04.320
Have you ever met someone

23:05.640 --> 23:07.480
with whom you're constantly afraid

23:08.720 --> 23:12.920
that one day she'll slip away
and never come back?

23:13.960 --> 23:15.200
Are you totally into her?

23:15.280 --> 23:18.440
I feel like I'm a bit of a wimp
in front of her.

23:18.520 --> 23:20.680
I can't say anything.

23:21.960 --> 23:24.800
I'm afraid
that if I say even one wrong word,

23:25.840 --> 23:27.320
she'll never talk to me again.

23:27.840 --> 23:29.760
Su Haoan. I can't believe there's
someone you don't dare to court,

23:29.840 --> 23:31.440
but I have to say,

23:32.520 --> 23:34.720
the more you don't dare,
the more you have to court her.

23:34.800 --> 23:36.360
Just in case you really lose her

23:36.440 --> 23:38.240
because you keep putting it off.

23:38.320 --> 23:40.880
Bro. I think I really need to talk.

23:42.120 --> 23:44.840
Tomorrow night, come to Overtime, okay?

23:45.640 --> 23:46.960
Lately, I'm not free at night.

23:47.040 --> 23:48.560
What are you busy with at night?

23:48.640 --> 23:51.120
I'm confirming something.

23:51.200 --> 23:53.000
Confirming what? Tell me.

23:53.080 --> 23:56.600
Recently, a girl wanted to hit on me,

23:57.760 --> 24:00.440
so I don't have time to deal
with other people's business.

24:00.520 --> 24:02.520
- Understand?
- It's fine if you don't tell me.

24:03.160 --> 24:05.440
I'm not in the mood
for your gossip today anyway.

24:05.520 --> 24:06.520
See you later.

24:08.280 --> 24:10.560
If you need anything, feel free to ask me.

24:10.640 --> 24:11.840
Maybe…

24:12.760 --> 24:13.920
Maybe I will have time.

24:15.520 --> 24:16.400
Got it.

24:17.720 --> 24:18.840
See you later.

24:41.760 --> 24:43.400
First Frost (Shuangjiang).

24:47.040 --> 24:49.120
Doesn't that mean Shuangjiang?

24:54.280 --> 24:56.160
Hello, everyone. My name is Wen Yifan.

24:56.760 --> 25:00.320
My hobby is dancing.
My nickname is Shuangjiang

25:01.000 --> 25:04.960
because the day
I was born was the first frost.

25:05.040 --> 25:06.720
Then my father gave me this nickname.

25:13.600 --> 25:15.360
So he always remembers it.

25:45.520 --> 25:47.280
Wen Shuangjiang.

25:54.120 --> 25:54.960
What's up?

25:55.760 --> 25:57.600
Nothing. So, you can hear me.

26:01.840 --> 26:02.880
Shuangjiang.

26:06.440 --> 26:08.000
I suddenly want to fall in love.

26:09.880 --> 26:12.560
In love with Sang Yan.

26:37.200 --> 26:38.400
Hey, Qiao.

26:38.480 --> 26:42.480
Happy birthday to you

26:42.560 --> 26:46.080
Happy birthday to you

26:46.720 --> 26:50.320
Happy birthday to you

26:50.400 --> 26:54.320
Happy birthday to you

26:54.400 --> 26:56.680
- Dian, happy birthday.
- Thank you.

26:56.760 --> 26:59.920
I held off all night and tried hard
to wait until 12:00 to say this.

27:00.000 --> 27:01.360
How's that? Am I the first?

27:03.240 --> 27:05.480
Are you free tomorrow?
I'll treat you to dinner.

27:06.480 --> 27:08.880
- Are you free now?
- Right now?

27:09.600 --> 27:10.480
PIZZA HUT

27:11.000 --> 27:14.760
What are you doing tomorrow?
Why does it have to be today?

27:15.760 --> 27:16.720
I have something on my mind.

27:16.800 --> 27:20.080
If I don't figure it out tonight,
I might not be able to sleep.

27:20.160 --> 27:22.400
What's that? Why is it so serious?

27:26.360 --> 27:28.480
It's my first time in this situation,

27:28.560 --> 27:30.360
so I don't have much experience.

27:31.040 --> 27:31.920
I want to be straight,

27:32.000 --> 27:35.040
but I'm afraid he'll think
I'm up to something else.

27:36.880 --> 27:39.680
What are you talking about?
Who are you plotting against?

27:40.480 --> 27:41.600
No.

27:45.440 --> 27:48.440
I want to court Sang Yan.

27:50.240 --> 27:52.000
Really?

27:52.600 --> 27:54.120
Keep your voice down.

27:54.200 --> 27:56.640
So, you finally figured it out?

27:57.160 --> 27:59.000
Doing your best to woo him?
I'm definitely behind you.

27:59.080 --> 28:01.280
- Really?
- Of course.

28:01.360 --> 28:02.920
Since we met,

28:03.000 --> 28:05.280
I've never heard of you
trying to woo someone.

28:07.200 --> 28:09.320
Actually, I'm glad you told me that.

28:10.040 --> 28:11.080
We're close,

28:11.160 --> 28:13.960
but you never share
what's on your mind with me.

28:15.200 --> 28:16.080
I'm sorry.

28:16.760 --> 28:17.920
I didn't blame you.

28:18.680 --> 28:20.920
Tell me. Do you have any plans
to court Sang Yan?

28:21.840 --> 28:25.040
I don't have any, so I wanted to ask you.

28:26.320 --> 28:28.680
I don't like your type.

28:29.560 --> 28:30.400
What's my type?

28:30.480 --> 28:32.000
I'm passionate. You don't like me?

28:33.080 --> 28:34.520
You're sticking to me too much.

28:35.320 --> 28:37.320
He may not like too passionate courting.

28:39.440 --> 28:42.720
Then you can't be too passionate,
but not too subtle either.

28:44.160 --> 28:45.480
That's too difficult.

28:47.880 --> 28:50.240
But I think
the biggest difficulty is still

28:50.320 --> 28:51.520
that I don't have the courage.

28:52.920 --> 28:55.000
Wen Yifan. I won't allow you
to say that about yourself.

28:55.080 --> 28:57.200
Who says you don't have courage?

28:57.280 --> 28:58.720
You've never relied on your family

28:58.800 --> 29:01.720
or given your friends any trouble.

29:01.800 --> 29:04.280
You've solved everything on your own.

29:04.800 --> 29:08.040
In my opinion,
you're the bravest girl I know.

29:08.120 --> 29:10.480
That's like the sauce in this pizza.

29:10.560 --> 29:13.920
If it doesn't form strands,
it won't taste good,

29:14.000 --> 29:17.840
so you have to lay some strands
on him every now and then

29:17.920 --> 29:20.320
to make him feel like you care about him.

29:20.400 --> 29:21.920
That way, he'll need you.

29:22.000 --> 29:25.360
That's like a spider's web
he can't escape from.

29:26.080 --> 29:28.200
Then, wait for him to confess to you.
How's that?

29:29.480 --> 29:30.320
Is it really possible?

29:31.240 --> 29:32.440
I think so.

29:33.920 --> 29:35.800
Anyway, whatever you decide,

29:35.880 --> 29:38.120
I wish you a stunning success.
Once and for all.

29:47.440 --> 29:49.440
I want to be desperate this time

29:49.520 --> 29:52.880
and run to that person
without thinking about anything.

29:55.200 --> 29:57.960
I also want to try
to be that passionate person.

30:00.400 --> 30:03.120
I don't think it matters if I fail.

30:11.400 --> 30:15.040
I want to try at least once.

30:18.040 --> 30:19.520
I want to court Sang Yan.

30:25.680 --> 30:28.440
The light is still on.
He doesn't seem to be sleeping.

30:31.080 --> 30:33.320
THANK YOU FOR THE GIFT

30:38.760 --> 30:40.000
THANK YOU

30:52.080 --> 30:53.000
Get an early night.

30:59.040 --> 31:00.200
Get an early night.

31:04.720 --> 31:06.040
So,

31:08.200 --> 31:12.560
on your birthday,
I'll give you a gift back.

31:13.840 --> 31:15.240
If he agrees,

31:15.320 --> 31:19.440
even if he moves out then,
I'll have a reason to talk to him again.

31:23.160 --> 31:24.080
Uh-huh.

31:26.440 --> 31:27.720
Uh-huh?

31:49.920 --> 31:51.920
There are 69 days left.

31:56.160 --> 31:58.400
There are 69 days left.

31:58.480 --> 32:01.200
There are 69 days left.

32:02.160 --> 32:04.800
There are 69 days left.

32:10.720 --> 32:15.240
If it's okay, can you give me
a countdown every day?

32:29.160 --> 32:31.000
I'm afraid I'll forget.

32:34.240 --> 32:35.600
Why are you so cheeky?

32:35.680 --> 32:37.640
Can't you be a little sincere?

32:37.720 --> 32:41.640
It's something
You should remember this all the time

32:41.720 --> 32:44.000
instead of asking me
to remind you once a day.

32:44.080 --> 32:45.120
Understand?

32:52.520 --> 32:53.880
OK. I'll remember.

32:55.000 --> 32:56.560
OK. I'll remember.

33:21.360 --> 33:22.600
Then…

33:22.680 --> 33:25.160
Do I need to remember your birthday later?

33:28.160 --> 33:31.680
January 2nd, Capricorn,
but I don't like celebrating birthdays.

33:46.280 --> 33:48.120
Guo's been nice to you, Tian.

33:48.960 --> 33:51.000
He even arranged this for you
while you were in labor.

33:52.200 --> 33:53.120
Of course.

33:53.200 --> 33:56.000
He said he'd help me and love me well

33:56.080 --> 33:58.000
and bought me those four things.

33:59.120 --> 34:01.240
As long as he's good to you and the baby.

34:01.320 --> 34:02.320
Yifan.

34:02.840 --> 34:06.280
Did you wear perfume today?
This smells good.

34:06.360 --> 34:07.280
Really?

34:12.239 --> 34:15.600
I feel like you're a little off today.
Are you in love?

34:17.880 --> 34:19.199
No, I'm not.

34:23.280 --> 34:24.440
I've been courting someone lately.

34:25.040 --> 34:27.760
What? You're courting someone?

34:30.679 --> 34:33.800
I didn't realize
even you would be so proactive.

34:35.080 --> 34:38.440
Yifan. You should know
that you're very good,

34:38.520 --> 34:41.159
so you must make more choices.
Don't make do.

34:41.239 --> 34:43.360
I'm not making do. He's very nice,

34:44.679 --> 34:46.320
and he's very good-looking.

34:46.960 --> 34:48.199
How good-looking?

34:48.280 --> 34:49.480
He's good enough

34:52.120 --> 34:54.280
to be on a restaurant sign.

34:55.639 --> 34:57.480
On a restaurant sign?

35:00.520 --> 35:01.480
How do you feel?

35:04.280 --> 35:06.520
By the way, this is for you.

35:07.200 --> 35:08.240
I can't take it.

35:08.760 --> 35:11.520
Don't say that. Guo told me so. Come on.

35:13.000 --> 35:15.320
- Thanks, Tian.
- You're welcome.

35:15.400 --> 35:17.960
If he's that good, you can't lose to him.

35:18.040 --> 35:19.720
I forgot to tell you

35:19.800 --> 35:21.960
this guy is my roommate.

35:22.720 --> 35:25.120
We're at home every day,
so we know all of each other's faults.

35:25.960 --> 35:27.560
Your roommate?

35:27.640 --> 35:30.480
That guy?
"I hope you're as happy as I am"?

35:32.560 --> 35:34.320
Oh my God.

35:34.400 --> 35:36.720
No. I've got to get back
to the labor center.

35:36.800 --> 35:38.320
This story is going too…

35:38.400 --> 35:40.280
I need to sort it out.

35:41.160 --> 35:43.960
Yifan. You're amazing.

35:44.040 --> 35:45.600
Listen, you're no worse than him.

35:47.000 --> 35:50.320
You must love someone
as proudly as he does, okay?

35:52.640 --> 35:54.320
The next job is…

35:54.400 --> 35:58.720
Gu, you two,
arrange the next research work.

35:58.800 --> 36:00.600
Actually, Ms. Cao,

36:00.680 --> 36:02.400
the planner gave some comments

36:02.480 --> 36:04.040
on the operation plan
for this holiday event,

36:04.120 --> 36:06.480
so we may have to improve it.

36:08.720 --> 36:09.600
SANG YAN

36:09.680 --> 36:11.080
I will go back later today.

36:13.800 --> 36:15.280
But in this regard,

36:15.360 --> 36:18.040
our team is very active with them,

36:18.120 --> 36:20.480
so we hope you can give us more time.

36:20.560 --> 36:22.640
Right. As for the programs,
we've done three,

36:22.720 --> 36:23.800
but they need to be implemented

36:23.880 --> 36:27.560
in a concrete way so that we can see
which one is more suitable for us.

36:39.360 --> 36:42.400
You have to lay some strands
on him every now and then

36:43.000 --> 36:45.400
to make him feel like you care about him.

36:45.480 --> 36:47.000
That way, he'll need you.

36:47.080 --> 36:50.760
That's like a spider's web
he can't escape from.

36:56.920 --> 36:59.280
WEIBO FOLLOWING

37:01.640 --> 37:03.880
DEAR SHUDONG

37:17.480 --> 37:21.800
HOW DO I COURT SOMEONE I'VE OFFENDED?

37:27.960 --> 37:30.360
DEAR SHUDONG

37:32.240 --> 37:36.040
IT'S THE EASIEST TO COURT
SOMEONE YOU'VE OFFENDED!

37:37.200 --> 37:39.040
YOU HAVE FOND MEMORIES

37:39.120 --> 37:42.720
DON'T BE EMBARRASSED
THAT'S WHAT MAKES YOU FALL IN LOVE

37:48.280 --> 37:51.440
Over here is our planning team.
Over there is the art team.

37:51.520 --> 37:53.400
Over here is the program team.

38:12.320 --> 38:13.360
Sixty-eight days to go.

38:17.800 --> 38:20.960
I'M AFRAID I'LL FORGET

38:25.280 --> 38:29.400
DON'T YOU WANT ME TO MEMORIZE IT MYSELF?

38:31.480 --> 38:34.080
Will he still send me messages?

38:35.760 --> 38:38.280
If I fall asleep again, I won't get that.

39:14.840 --> 39:18.800
True, but you're good at muddling through.

39:19.520 --> 39:21.240
You've said you'd treat me
several times before,

39:21.320 --> 39:22.720
but you haven't repaid it till now.

39:22.800 --> 39:24.040
If I don't remind you,

39:24.560 --> 39:28.560
you'll probably ignore what you said
in the same way.

39:29.160 --> 39:30.480
I'll lose out in the end.

39:30.560 --> 39:32.120
SANG YAN

39:32.200 --> 39:35.120
Don't you want me to remind you every day?

39:36.120 --> 39:40.080
THEN, DOES THE COOKING I GAVE YOU
SEVERAL TIMES BEFORE COUNT AS REPAYMENT?

39:46.360 --> 39:49.600
Okay. Then, what do you want to eat?

39:51.560 --> 39:52.880
I'll repay you.

39:53.720 --> 39:56.760
I WON'T LET YOU SUFFER LOSS

40:00.240 --> 40:02.000
The only value I have
was already plundered by you,

40:02.760 --> 40:04.280
so how can I have the room
for losing out more?

40:23.840 --> 40:26.600
The only value I have
was already plundered by you,

40:26.680 --> 40:27.920
so how can I have the room
for losing out more?

40:30.880 --> 40:34.680
So, does he see me as the lusting girl
people mentioned on the Internet?

40:34.760 --> 40:35.800
What did I do?

40:36.320 --> 40:37.680
You swooped in,

40:38.560 --> 40:39.600
hugged me,

40:40.560 --> 40:41.440
and kissed me.

40:56.640 --> 40:58.200
You're not taking liberties
with me this time?

41:10.560 --> 41:13.000
If I keep being so enthusiastic
while sleepwalking,

41:14.120 --> 41:16.680
will he lose his freshness for me?

41:21.040 --> 41:24.360
What to do, Dian? It's so shameful.

41:25.160 --> 41:26.800
Are you ashamed, too?

41:53.840 --> 41:59.080
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

41:59.160 --> 42:01.640
Where would hiding it
make it more of a surprise?

42:38.880 --> 42:40.160
The present is on the shelf.

42:56.200 --> 42:57.200
Happy birthday.

45:42.360 --> 45:43.200
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:43.280 --> 45:44.120
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
